<p>△ 《Mostly wood》by Nejc Polovsak</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="腾讯万字干货！2020-2021 设计趋势报告：多媒体篇" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-385434" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/uisdc-dt-20200820-32.gif" width="638" height="342" /></span></p>
