<p>△ 《ACE OF SPADES》 by Tony Babel</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="腾讯万字干货！2020-2021 设计趋势报告：多媒体篇" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-385457" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/uisdc-dt-20200820-55.gif" width="638" height="342" /></span></p>
<p>△ 《Can of worms》 by Tony Babel</p>
<p><strong>7. 更克制的色调与秩序感</strong></p>
<p>在充斥着各式各样的新鲜元素的当下，节奏更快颜色更有吸引力，各类信息视觉都在捕捉你的视线。干净的色调、简单的视觉、真实的肌理、强调秩序感的动画的出现，使得人在视觉上获得了极致舒适的体验，很大程度上缓解了极速发展的时代所带给人们的焦虑。</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="腾讯万字干货！2020-2021 设计趋势报告：多媒体篇" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-385458" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/uisdc-dt-20200820-56.gif" width="638" height="342" /></span></p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="腾讯万字干货！2020-2021 设计趋势报告：多媒体篇" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-385459" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/uisdc-dt-20200820-57.gif" width="638" height="342" /></span></p>
<p>△ 《BIC》by Artem &#8216;Hinz&#8217; Yudin</p>
<p><span class="img-zoom"><img alt="腾讯万字干货！2020-2021 设计趋势报告：多媒体篇" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-385460" src="https://image.uisdc.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/uisdc-dt-20200820-58.gif" width="638" height="342" /></span></p>
